##Doxygen Testing


This repository contains the Employees project, documented using **Doxygen** to generate HTML documentation directly from annotated source code. The purpose of this project is to demonstrate proper software documentation practices using Doxygen.


##project Overview

The Employees project consists of C++ source files that define employee-related classes and functionality. All files, classes, methods, and functions have been documented usig Doxygen0style comments so that documentation can be generated automatically.


##Documentation Generation

Doxygen is used to generate the documentation for this project.

